lead_paragraph: Stephan Jaeger backed up his record 12-under 58 with a 65 on Friday, giving him a five-stroke lead halfway through the Web.com Tour's Ellie Mae Classic.

headline.print_headline: Stephan Jaeger Follows Record 58 With 65 on Web.com Tour
